WEBVTT

01:37.860 --> 01:41.009
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.080 --> 01:43.970
[Episode 17]

01:49.810 --> 01:50.900
Watch the heat.

01:55.430 --> 01:59.580
[Xue Rui]
[The Yan Du Xian is well-received, right?]

01:58.680 --> 01:59.509
Very good.

02:01.310 --> 02:02.350
Hurry up.

02:02.480 --> 02:02.840
Okay.

02:02.840 --> 02:04.840
-No problem at all.
-Qiaoqi! Qiaoqi!

02:04.840 --> 02:07.510
A customer is causing trouble
in the Chinese restaurant.

02:07.510 --> 02:08.750
Go find the restaurant manager.

02:08.750 --> 02:09.610
Why look for me?

02:09.610 --> 02:10.270
Because...

02:11.840 --> 02:12.520
Because...

02:14.310 --> 02:16.030
You secretly changed the chef

02:16.030 --> 02:17.890
without informing us customers!

02:17.960 --> 02:19.520
If I hadn't asked just now,

02:19.520 --> 02:20.800
were you going to keep hiding it?

02:20.800 --> 02:22.079
It's not like that, sir.

02:22.079 --> 02:23.030
Our official website has already...

02:23.030 --> 02:23.850
Close it!

02:24.280 --> 02:25.520
Official website?

02:25.520 --> 02:27.520
I'm here to have a meal.
Why would I check the website?

02:27.520 --> 02:29.130
What's so great about your place?

02:29.130 --> 02:30.870
The Imperial Kitchen, huh?

02:31.310 --> 02:32.000
Well, sir,

02:32.090 --> 02:32.680
I am

02:32.680 --> 02:34.680
the manager of the Chinese restaurant.

02:34.680 --> 02:36.120
If you are not satisfied

02:36.120 --> 02:37.190
with our Yan Du Xian,

02:37.190 --> 02:38.310
we can replace it

02:38.310 --> 02:39.520
with another dish for free.

02:39.520 --> 02:41.450
The other dishes are also very good

02:41.840 --> 02:42.310
and delicious.

02:42.310 --> 02:43.000
Look, everyone!

02:43.000 --> 02:43.710
Look!

02:44.030 --> 02:45.750
They have a guilty conscience!

02:45.750 --> 02:47.840
They know their food is terrible,

02:47.840 --> 02:48.910
so they do this,

02:48.910 --> 02:50.840
trying to buy their way out.

02:50.840 --> 02:52.280
Is the Chinese restaurant at Purong Hotel

02:52.280 --> 02:53.560
only at this level?

02:53.560 --> 02:56.470
And you claim to be a time-honored brand
in Shanghai, huh?

02:56.470 --> 02:58.750
-Our Chinese restaurant's...
-Excuse me, do you have any complaints

02:58.750 --> 03:00.480
about the Chinese restaurant?

03:05.560 --> 03:06.190
Sir.

03:06.470 --> 03:08.000
I'm the acting chef of Purong Hotel,

03:08.000 --> 03:08.840
Li Qiaoqi.

03:09.120 --> 03:10.750
What do you think about our dishes?

03:10.750 --> 03:12.030
Please tell me.

03:14.840 --> 03:16.560
Your chef is a little girl?

03:17.310 --> 03:18.310
That explains it.

03:20.240 --> 03:21.030
Sir,

03:21.430 --> 03:23.690
my cooking might not have satisfied you.

03:23.790 --> 03:24.960
Please give me your suggestions.

03:24.960 --> 03:26.490
I will definitely improve.

03:26.520 --> 03:27.079
Come on! Come on!

03:27.079 --> 03:28.360
Take a look, everyone.

03:28.680 --> 03:31.840
The former head chef of Purong Hotel,
Jia Shikun,

03:32.079 --> 03:33.430
has job-hopped.

03:33.800 --> 03:35.520
I was wondering

03:36.240 --> 03:37.079
why such a famous master

03:37.079 --> 03:39.430
of Huaiyang cuisine

03:39.430 --> 03:41.960
couldn't continue working at Purong Hotel.

03:42.310 --> 03:45.030
So, there's a young and beautiful
female chef

03:45.030 --> 03:46.680
waiting to get promoted, huh?

03:46.680 --> 03:47.590
What a pity.

03:48.590 --> 03:50.310
She only has good looks.

03:50.310 --> 03:52.000
But her skills are

03:54.280 --> 03:57.310
far inferior to Master Jia's.

03:57.870 --> 03:58.670
Sir,

03:59.250 --> 04:01.590
if you have complaints about my food,
just say it.

04:01.590 --> 04:03.310
Isn't a personal attack
a bit inappropriate?

04:03.310 --> 04:05.400
What? I'm unsatisfied with the food.

04:05.400 --> 04:06.310
Can't I complain about it?

04:06.310 --> 04:07.280
Is there a problem?

04:07.280 --> 04:09.030
Your food is bad,

04:09.470 --> 04:10.430
but you blame your customers?

04:10.430 --> 04:11.470
With this service attitude,

04:11.470 --> 04:13.030
I'll record it and post it all online!

04:13.030 --> 04:13.560
Come on.

04:15.970 --> 04:16.560
Sir,

04:16.959 --> 04:17.959
please calm down.

04:20.240 --> 04:22.010
I came all the way here

04:22.029 --> 04:25.120
just to have some authentic Yan Du Xian.

04:25.560 --> 04:26.390
But what do I get?

04:26.390 --> 04:27.850
Your service is terrible.

04:27.870 --> 04:29.870
And you even want to hit people, huh?

04:30.600 --> 04:31.920
Sir, I'm sorry.

04:32.310 --> 04:33.830
We've let you down.

04:34.130 --> 04:36.930
I apologize on behalf of our hotel.

04:37.120 --> 04:38.870
I will comp your Yan Du Xian.

04:39.220 --> 04:41.220
You can try some other dishes.

04:42.330 --> 04:43.730
I'm not trying anything.

04:44.430 --> 04:45.960
I didn't get to eat the food,

04:46.430 --> 04:48.030
but I am seething with anger.

04:48.830 --> 04:49.720
I'm leaving.

04:52.310 --> 04:53.000
Sir, you...

04:53.430 --> 04:54.120
Qiaoqi.

04:58.870 --> 05:00.160
I'm sorry. I'm sorry

05:00.340 --> 05:01.040
I'm sorry,

05:01.040 --> 05:02.300
ladies and gentlemen.

05:02.870 --> 05:04.310
I'm sorry for interrupting your meal.

05:04.310 --> 05:05.370
We are truly sorry.

05:06.120 --> 05:07.720
Today's Yan Du Xian

05:07.720 --> 05:09.480
is cooked

05:09.480 --> 05:11.620
by our new chef.

05:12.040 --> 05:14.040
Compared to the previous Yan Du Xian,

05:14.040 --> 05:15.270
the taste is slightly different,

05:15.270 --> 05:16.720
but they both have their merits.

05:16.720 --> 05:17.430
So,

05:17.430 --> 05:18.920
today, we would like to invite you to

05:18.920 --> 05:20.430
try it for free.

05:20.430 --> 05:21.480
We hope you can give us

05:21.480 --> 05:22.920
your valuable feedback.

05:23.600 --> 05:24.200
Thank you.

05:24.310 --> 05:24.910
Thank you.

05:25.630 --> 05:27.430
Please continue with your meal.

05:36.750 --> 05:38.270
Why did you comp his meal?

05:38.270 --> 05:39.920
Is the food I cook worthless?

05:39.920 --> 05:40.560
Qiaoqi,

05:41.210 --> 05:42.710
there is no problem with your food.

05:42.710 --> 05:43.870
But in that situation just now,

05:43.870 --> 05:45.920
it wasn't the place to reason with him.

05:45.920 --> 05:46.630
You saw it.

05:46.650 --> 05:48.600
That diner was here to cause trouble.

05:48.600 --> 05:49.600
You knew he was looking for trouble,

05:49.600 --> 05:50.800
so why did you do that?

05:51.159 --> 05:52.390
By comping his meal like this,

05:52.390 --> 05:54.430
it only makes it look like I was wrong.

05:54.430 --> 05:55.740
That's not what I meant.

05:55.740 --> 05:56.830
Excuse me.

05:56.830 --> 05:57.890
What are you doing?

05:58.040 --> 05:59.880
This is the food returned by the customer.

05:59.880 --> 06:01.450
I'll eat it for you.

06:01.600 --> 06:02.330
What a waste.

06:05.830 --> 06:06.830
Don't follow me.

06:18.330 --> 06:20.730
Hello, this is
Purong Chinese Restaurant.

06:20.860 --> 06:22.590
Okay, I've canceled it for you.

06:24.510 --> 06:25.190
Good job.

06:27.360 --> 06:28.830
Hold them off for a few more days

06:28.830 --> 06:30.180
until they are completely dead.

06:30.180 --> 06:30.860
By the way,

06:31.270 --> 06:32.390
tell Chef Jia

06:32.750 --> 06:34.310
to deadlock the salted meat channel

06:34.310 --> 06:35.240
over this period

06:35.830 --> 06:36.750
at all costs.

06:40.250 --> 06:43.260
[Sales Analysis]

06:50.470 --> 06:52.960
[Purong Chinese Restaurant]

06:50.740 --> 06:51.400
Mr. Ji,

06:51.550 --> 06:53.510
our rating on the platform
has dropped below 4.

06:53.510 --> 06:55.370
It can't make it to the front page.

06:59.100 --> 07:00.580
Excuse me. Excuse me.

07:00.600 --> 07:01.310
Excuse me.

07:04.190 --> 07:04.950
Qiaoqi,

07:05.280 --> 07:06.410
they're all rotten.

07:09.500 --> 07:11.100
Hurry up and throw them away.

07:14.690 --> 07:15.760
What a pity.

07:21.310 --> 07:23.300
The food quality is so disappointing.

07:23.300 --> 07:24.950
The dining environment is just so-so.

07:24.950 --> 07:25.950
The service attitude is not good either.

07:25.950 --> 07:27.750
How can it be a five-star hotel?

07:27.750 --> 07:28.950
It's even worse than the three-star ones.

07:28.950 --> 07:29.950
The store bullies customers.

07:29.950 --> 07:30.870
I'll never come here.

07:30.870 --> 07:31.510
Mr. Ji.

07:31.800 --> 07:33.220
What should we do now?

07:34.040 --> 07:35.270
Notify the Marketing Department.

07:35.270 --> 07:36.600
Tell them to give me

07:36.750 --> 07:38.350
a closing plan within a week.

07:40.190 --> 07:41.320
Chinese restaurant

07:41.430 --> 07:42.390
is suspended.

07:57.390 --> 07:57.950
Notice:

07:58.240 --> 08:00.040
the Chinese restaurant will be
temporarily closed this week.

08:00.040 --> 08:01.510
Foremen and forewomen of all floors
in the HSKP Department,

08:01.510 --> 08:03.040
should communicate well with the guests.

08:03.040 --> 08:04.840
Thank you for your cooperation.

08:10.670 --> 08:12.480
I called you here for a short meeting.

08:12.480 --> 08:13.160
Regarding

08:13.190 --> 08:14.960
the notice of the temporary closure of
the Chinese restaurant,

08:14.960 --> 08:16.070
the HSKP Department's work

08:16.070 --> 08:17.670
needs to make corresponding adjustments.

08:17.670 --> 08:18.750
The Chinese restaurant is closed down.

08:18.750 --> 08:19.950
Is Purong Hotel going to close down too?

08:19.950 --> 08:22.280
No way.
I've only been here for half a year.

08:22.590 --> 08:24.080
Regarding the rumors about
the Chinese restaurant,

08:24.080 --> 08:25.540
please do not spread them.

08:25.600 --> 08:27.130
As a member of Purong Hotel,

08:27.310 --> 08:28.160
I hope

08:28.510 --> 08:29.950
we can have more confidence

08:29.950 --> 08:31.000
and less panic.

08:31.070 --> 08:32.510
No matter how the leaders arrange it,

08:32.510 --> 08:33.150
as long as we

08:33.150 --> 08:34.630
do our own jobs well

08:34.630 --> 08:36.080
and provide good service,

08:36.080 --> 08:37.390
we will definitely be fine.

08:37.390 --> 08:38.270
Got it?

08:38.600 --> 08:39.530
-Got it.
-Got it.

08:43.630 --> 08:44.960
Welcome back next time.

09:06.230 --> 09:13.170
[Purong Hotel Chinese Restaurant
Temporarily Closed]

09:19.630 --> 09:21.500
The kitchen is so quiet today.

09:21.630 --> 09:23.610
I heard the chef quit.

09:23.630 --> 09:24.430
Yes, yes, yes.

09:24.630 --> 09:26.390
I heard the chef is a woman.

09:26.440 --> 09:27.750
How did she become the chef?

09:27.750 --> 09:28.750
She's not the official one.

09:28.750 --> 09:30.010
She's the acting chef.

09:30.150 --> 09:31.200
I think this woman

09:31.200 --> 09:32.890
is either related to the higher-ups,

09:32.890 --> 09:34.440
or the higher-ups use her as a tool,

09:34.440 --> 09:36.080
praising her first and then,
destroying her.

09:36.080 --> 09:37.750
Anyway, the Chinese restaurant is
in big trouble now.

09:37.750 --> 09:39.480
It's directly closed for good.

10:24.150 --> 10:25.630
Hurry up, brothers.

10:25.630 --> 10:26.560
Come on, come on.

11:11.450 --> 11:12.910
It's all my fault.

11:16.870 --> 11:19.210
It's all my fault.

11:28.070 --> 11:33.450
[Staff Only]

11:45.370 --> 11:46.780
[Management Analysis and Conclusion]

11:54.600 --> 11:55.150
Mr. Ji.

11:55.150 --> 11:57.680
I came to get your clothes
that need dry-cleaning.

11:57.680 --> 11:58.480
Wait a minute.

12:03.370 --> 12:04.040
Come on.

12:05.330 --> 12:06.010
Here you go.

12:08.030 --> 12:08.830
What's wrong?

12:08.900 --> 12:09.660
Are you okay?

12:10.770 --> 12:11.630
Are you crying?

12:19.270 --> 12:21.400
I just went to the Chinese restaurant.

12:22.360 --> 12:24.220
Today is the last day of business.

12:24.320 --> 12:25.480
I feel a little sad.

12:26.150 --> 12:27.610
The Chinese restaurant is

12:27.630 --> 12:28.870
temporarily closed.

12:29.360 --> 12:30.600
Temporary, okay?

12:31.720 --> 12:32.870
Why are you sad?

12:33.670 --> 12:34.750
Aren't you sad?

12:36.500 --> 12:38.720
Your comrades-in-arms are still
going through fire and water for you,

12:38.720 --> 12:41.440
but you have abandoned the city
and fled with your troops.

12:41.440 --> 12:42.030
If you act like this,

12:42.030 --> 12:44.160
how can anyone work together with you?

12:46.510 --> 12:47.390
Go on.

12:49.320 --> 12:51.200
Li Qiaoqi was promoted by you.

12:51.670 --> 12:52.390
You know

12:52.390 --> 12:54.520
her character and her cooking skills.

12:54.950 --> 12:57.550
The closure of the Chinese restaurant
has nothing to do with her.

12:57.550 --> 13:00.030
Why did you put her in the spotlight

13:00.670 --> 13:01.750
and let others trample on her

13:01.750 --> 13:02.790
and smear her?

13:05.630 --> 13:06.720
Do you mean

13:07.480 --> 13:08.150
I should have emphasized in

13:08.150 --> 13:10.280
the notice that
closing the Chinese restaurant

13:10.280 --> 13:11.360
has nothing to do

13:11.390 --> 13:12.750
with Li Qiaoqi

13:13.240 --> 13:13.840
and

13:13.840 --> 13:15.760
called on everyone not to cyberbully her?

13:15.760 --> 13:16.710
If I did that,

13:16.910 --> 13:18.970
Li Qiaoqi would leave with glory,

13:19.060 --> 13:20.010
and you would be satisfied then?

13:20.010 --> 13:20.520
Huh?

13:21.200 --> 13:22.000
Qiaoqi is

13:22.720 --> 13:23.960
the biggest victim

13:23.960 --> 13:24.960
in this incident,

13:25.120 --> 13:25.840
who was promoted by you,

13:25.840 --> 13:26.670
and then

13:26.690 --> 13:27.820
cut down.

13:28.060 --> 13:29.360
If it weren't for your whim,

13:29.360 --> 13:31.140
she wouldn't have been on
this roller coaster.

13:31.140 --> 13:33.530
She was a hero of the business banquet.

13:33.550 --> 13:35.150
But the next day, she became

13:35.150 --> 13:36.240
a despised chef who caused
the closure of the restaurant.

13:36.240 --> 13:37.870
Is it fair to her?

13:43.160 --> 13:43.760
Go on.

13:46.360 --> 13:47.330
I'm sorry.

13:48.160 --> 13:49.180
You asked me to speak.

13:49.180 --> 13:49.840
Chickened out?

13:49.840 --> 13:51.170
I'm not chickening out.

13:51.930 --> 13:54.010
I know I have no right to say this.

13:54.200 --> 13:55.800
I apologize for my attitude,

13:55.920 --> 13:57.250
but not for this matter.

14:01.040 --> 14:02.060
Do you know

14:02.350 --> 14:03.630
what the purpose of

14:03.840 --> 14:06.000
suspending the Chinese restaurant is?

14:06.000 --> 14:06.840
Do you know

14:06.960 --> 14:08.820
how many departments' interests

14:08.920 --> 14:10.880
will be affected
by this event

14:11.240 --> 14:12.750
and how many vested interests
will be intrigued?

14:12.750 --> 14:13.680
Do you know that?

14:14.120 --> 14:14.960
Do you know

14:14.960 --> 14:16.920
how much resistance there is
from top to bottom,

14:16.920 --> 14:18.650
and how much risk I have to take?

14:19.000 --> 14:20.020
Then why did you...

14:20.020 --> 14:20.670
Because

14:21.360 --> 14:24.160
this concerns the overall reform
of Purong Hotel,

14:24.180 --> 14:26.810
and even its life and death.

14:29.770 --> 14:31.170
That's all I can tell you.

14:31.600 --> 14:33.550
You don't need to know the rest.

14:33.630 --> 14:35.550
Then what is Li Qiaoqi?

14:36.040 --> 14:37.240
Is she a first-aid kit

14:37.600 --> 14:39.360
to fill the chef vacancy,

14:39.360 --> 14:41.480
or a pawn in your business empire?

14:41.500 --> 14:42.960
You shouldn't ask me this.

14:43.210 --> 14:44.870
You should go ask your friend.

14:45.200 --> 14:46.030
Ask her

14:46.060 --> 14:47.510
whether she wants to be a deserter

14:47.510 --> 14:48.600
at this time,

14:48.600 --> 14:49.240
or

14:49.600 --> 14:51.600
stay with us

14:51.630 --> 14:53.830
until the Chinese restaurant reopens.

14:54.310 --> 14:55.840
She is the one that
should make the decision.

14:55.840 --> 14:56.480
Not me.

14:58.200 --> 14:59.440
So,

15:01.360 --> 15:02.960
you're not going to fire her?

15:04.750 --> 15:06.630
You should have more confidence

15:07.270 --> 15:09.030
in your peers.

15:13.090 --> 15:13.760
Good night.

15:19.500 --> 15:20.340
Good night.

15:28.360 --> 15:28.960
Qiaoqi.

15:28.960 --> 15:29.750
Are you okay?

15:30.800 --> 15:32.010
[Resignation Letter]

15:37.260 --> 15:38.320
You're resigning?

15:38.850 --> 15:39.970
Give it back.

15:41.860 --> 15:42.500
Qiaoqi,

15:43.510 --> 15:44.510
don't make a decision so hastily.

15:44.510 --> 15:46.710
No need, I've thought it through.

15:46.790 --> 15:48.480
The Chinese restaurant failed in my hands.

15:48.480 --> 15:49.320
I really don't have the courage

15:49.320 --> 15:51.050
to face my colleagues anymore.

15:52.240 --> 15:54.080
Most of them have already left.

15:54.100 --> 15:55.540
As for those who barely stayed,

15:55.540 --> 15:56.240
I believe they

15:56.240 --> 15:57.120
definitely wouldn't want to

15:57.120 --> 15:59.190
work with an incompetent chef.

15:59.220 --> 16:01.020
Me leaving is best for everyone.

16:01.080 --> 16:01.960
As for you,

16:01.980 --> 16:03.450
you don't need to shed crocodile tears.

16:03.450 --> 16:04.840
As for the decision to
close the Chinese restaurant,

16:04.840 --> 16:06.510
you must have voted yes.

16:06.510 --> 16:07.240
A slap in the face

16:07.240 --> 16:08.110
and a pat on the back.

16:08.110 --> 16:09.120
What's the point?

16:10.120 --> 16:10.840
Qiaoqi,

16:11.480 --> 16:13.740
I know the rumors in the hotel
are against you,

16:13.740 --> 16:15.520
but you really misunderstood.

16:22.250 --> 16:22.770
Look.

16:23.840 --> 16:24.530
What's this?

16:24.530 --> 16:25.910
It's the Marketing Department's
data analysis

16:25.910 --> 16:28.910
on the Chinese restaurant's
last month of operation.

16:29.630 --> 16:30.240
Look.

16:31.300 --> 16:32.470
Numbers don't lie.

16:32.470 --> 16:33.080
Qiaoqi,

16:33.150 --> 16:34.600
during your time as executive chef,

16:34.600 --> 16:35.720
the occupancy rate in the dining room

16:35.720 --> 16:37.720
has increased significantly
compared to before.

16:37.630 --> 16:40.400
[Purong Chinese Restaurant
Sales Data Analysis Statistical Chart]

16:37.720 --> 16:39.920
Look at the main hall's occupancy rate.

16:40.600 --> 16:41.720
Then, what dropped?

16:41.720 --> 16:43.890
It's the occupancy rate of
private rooms and the banquet hall.

16:43.890 --> 16:44.370
Look.

16:44.000 --> 16:45.660
[Purong Chinese Restaurant
Sales Data Analysis Statistical Chart]

16:44.400 --> 16:45.320
It's getting lower and lower.

16:45.320 --> 16:47.480
But the cancellation of orders for
the banquet hall and private rooms

16:47.480 --> 16:49.480
was basically related to
the personnel changes

16:49.480 --> 16:50.240
of our hotel.

16:50.360 --> 16:53.160
It has nothing to do with
the quality of our dishes.

16:54.630 --> 16:55.240
Besides,

16:55.420 --> 16:58.000
the internal questionnaire of
the F&B Department shows

16:58.000 --> 16:59.320
that the customer satisfaction rate

16:59.320 --> 17:00.360
is far higher than

16:59.350 --> 17:02.270
[Purong Chinese Restaurant
Sales Data Analysis Statistical Chart]

17:00.360 --> 17:01.870
the hotel's standard.

17:01.870 --> 17:02.620
So,

17:02.730 --> 17:03.950
when you said

17:04.510 --> 17:06.750
the Chinese restaurant
failed in your hands,

17:06.750 --> 17:07.970
or even that

17:08.310 --> 17:10.480
you ruined the whole Chinese restaurant
alone,

17:10.480 --> 17:11.510
I think such words

17:11.510 --> 17:12.720
are nonsense.

17:16.020 --> 17:16.900
Qiaoqi,

17:17.500 --> 17:18.710
Mr. Ji and I

17:19.089 --> 17:20.410
won't let these rumors

17:20.599 --> 17:21.930
dictate your future.

17:25.119 --> 17:26.319
Is this all true?

17:26.349 --> 17:27.670
Numbers never lie.

17:31.250 --> 17:32.620
That's great.

17:36.780 --> 17:38.310
Thank you, Xue Rui.

17:54.200 --> 17:55.350
If I really have to point out

17:55.350 --> 17:56.830
your shortcoming, Chef Li,

17:56.830 --> 17:58.000
it might be that you

17:58.000 --> 17:58.960
do not have

17:59.270 --> 18:00.400
the management perspective

18:00.400 --> 18:01.830
that an executive chef should have.

18:01.830 --> 18:03.000
But in the future,

18:03.000 --> 18:04.720
you just need to
strengthen your leadership.

18:04.720 --> 18:05.440
I believe

18:05.440 --> 18:06.480
you can lead the team well

18:06.480 --> 18:07.240
and let everyone fight together.

18:07.240 --> 18:08.200
I will, Mr. Ji.

18:08.270 --> 18:09.510
Thank you for your trust.

18:09.510 --> 18:12.010
Now that the Chinese restaurant is closed,

18:12.180 --> 18:13.050
you can

18:13.080 --> 18:14.720
concentrate on
developing your signature dishes.

18:14.720 --> 18:16.750
As long as the signature is established,

18:16.750 --> 18:18.550
I think the appeal of
our Chinese restaurant

18:18.550 --> 18:19.110
will be great.

18:19.110 --> 18:21.480
I'm going to look for
new suppliers tomorrow.

18:21.480 --> 18:23.590
I plan to look around
the nearby suburban counties

18:23.590 --> 18:26.350
to see if there are
any suitable cured pork suppliers.

18:26.350 --> 18:27.110
Hurry up.

18:27.110 --> 18:28.000
We are waiting for your good news.

18:28.000 --> 18:28.480
Okay.

18:32.960 --> 18:33.510
Mr. Ji,

18:33.530 --> 18:34.830
the board is ready.

18:34.830 --> 18:36.240
Are you going now?

18:38.240 --> 18:38.720
Yes.

18:39.830 --> 18:44.870
[Purong Chinese Restaurant
Total Profit Statement]

18:40.110 --> 18:41.640
The decision to close

18:41.660 --> 18:42.960
and renovate the Chinese restaurant

18:42.960 --> 18:45.090
was made based on our market research.

18:45.960 --> 18:47.640
These are the successful cases

18:47.640 --> 18:49.570
we have collected in recent years.

18:52.480 --> 18:53.400
The closure of the Chinese restaurant

18:53.400 --> 18:54.680
seemed to be

18:55.160 --> 18:56.860
caused by the departure of

18:57.160 --> 18:58.510
the star chef.

18:59.030 --> 19:00.070
But in fact,

19:00.550 --> 19:02.600
it was caused by the deep-rooted

19:02.650 --> 19:03.510
management problems

19:03.510 --> 19:05.310
within our Chinese restaurant.

19:07.240 --> 19:09.000
So this renovation

19:08.860 --> 19:12.020
[Wei Siyuan]

19:09.000 --> 19:11.790
is by no means
a superficial cleaning project,

19:12.220 --> 19:15.750
but a deep self-reflection.

19:18.680 --> 19:19.720
Sounds good.

19:20.570 --> 19:21.130
Let's go.

19:23.220 --> 19:24.660
[Thank You For Listening]

19:24.680 --> 19:26.000
[Quality Chinese Food Wins Reputation.
Excellent Service Creates The Future]

19:25.480 --> 19:26.240
Thank you, everyone.

19:26.030 --> 19:33.110
[Purong Hotel]

19:33.180 --> 19:35.580
[Thank You For Listening]

19:34.480 --> 19:35.880
When I heard that

19:35.630 --> 19:36.670
[Purong Hotel]

19:35.880 --> 19:37.070
the Chinese restaurant

19:37.070 --> 19:38.790
was closed for reconstruction,

19:38.790 --> 19:40.000
I was worried.

19:40.830 --> 19:41.590
But

19:41.670 --> 19:43.600
after reading this business plan,

19:43.750 --> 19:44.950
I felt much relieved.

19:45.720 --> 19:46.920
In my humble opinion,

19:46.960 --> 19:47.640
we should

19:47.670 --> 19:49.080
give young people

19:49.100 --> 19:50.300
more opportunities.

19:53.270 --> 19:54.160
Opportunities are

19:54.160 --> 19:55.820
always accompanied by risks.

19:56.360 --> 19:57.320
Your company

19:57.340 --> 19:58.820
only holds 4% of

19:58.850 --> 20:00.380
the shares in Purong Hotel.

20:00.790 --> 20:01.720
It's hard for you to understand

20:01.720 --> 20:03.250
our concerns.

20:03.480 --> 20:05.310
Rushing to renovate the Chinese restaurant

20:05.310 --> 20:06.240
is very likely

20:06.310 --> 20:07.720
to let investors' money

20:07.720 --> 20:08.720
go down the drain.

20:10.100 --> 20:11.750
After all, they are not paying

20:11.750 --> 20:14.180
to sponsor our renovation.

20:15.830 --> 20:16.770
As the old saying goes,

20:16.770 --> 20:18.590
preparation is the key to success.

20:18.590 --> 20:20.780
After the Chinese restaurant is renovated,

20:20.780 --> 20:22.930
if it can stimulate consumption

20:22.960 --> 20:23.950
and boost business,

20:23.950 --> 20:24.910
in the long run,

20:24.940 --> 20:27.060
it will be good for Purong Hotel.

20:27.160 --> 20:27.950
Mr. Gu,

20:27.980 --> 20:30.020
stop sitting on the fence.

20:30.040 --> 20:31.750
If you really had to pay for it,

20:31.790 --> 20:32.790
you definitely wouldn't do it.

20:32.790 --> 20:33.400
You...

20:35.400 --> 20:36.260
Siyuan.

20:36.560 --> 20:38.570
You are on the frontlines of
hotel management.

20:38.570 --> 20:39.840
Tell us your opinion.

20:40.030 --> 20:42.510
I can't be considered
on the frontlines anymore.

20:42.510 --> 20:44.250
The one really leading the charge is

20:44.250 --> 20:45.420
Mr. Ji.

20:45.690 --> 20:46.550
But to be honest,

20:46.550 --> 20:47.890
I just took a look.

20:47.910 --> 20:50.140
This renovation will cost 5 million.

20:50.740 --> 20:51.460
Mr. Ji,

20:51.750 --> 20:53.260
please don't take offense.

20:53.260 --> 20:55.660
I certainly believe you didn't overquote.

20:55.790 --> 20:58.400
But for the hotel, this expense is not

20:58.830 --> 21:00.030
a small amount.

21:00.830 --> 21:02.100
Ultimately,

21:02.270 --> 21:03.070
for a Chinese restaurant,

21:03.070 --> 21:04.170
the taste of the dishes is

21:04.170 --> 21:05.260
the most important.

21:05.260 --> 21:07.300
I suggest we endure it if we can.

21:07.440 --> 21:09.840
Taking a step back
will make things easier.

21:13.750 --> 21:14.960
It's too late.

21:15.810 --> 21:16.860
Guys.

21:16.920 --> 21:17.780
I'm late.

21:17.880 --> 21:18.250
[Duan Aoxiang]

21:18.510 --> 21:19.640
Mr. Duan Jr. is here.

21:21.160 --> 21:21.720
Madam.

21:21.860 --> 21:23.150
This is Mr. Duan Jr.

21:23.180 --> 21:24.680
He is an observer for the board.

21:24.680 --> 21:26.090
He doesn't participate in decision-making.

21:26.090 --> 21:28.900
Mr. Duan, you came here at this time.

21:28.990 --> 21:30.250
Do you have any advice?

21:30.250 --> 21:31.790
I wouldn't dare give advice.

21:31.790 --> 21:33.750
I'm here to learn from you seniors.

21:33.780 --> 21:34.420
By the way,

21:34.790 --> 21:35.720
I am

21:35.720 --> 21:37.050
a warm-hearted person.

21:37.440 --> 21:38.880
I heard about Mr. Ji's

21:38.880 --> 21:40.030
Chinese restaurant renovation plan,

21:40.030 --> 21:41.160
and I just couldn't sit still.

21:41.160 --> 21:42.040
There are some things

21:42.040 --> 21:43.180
I need to get off my chest.

21:43.180 --> 21:43.820
Mr. Ji,

21:44.570 --> 21:45.230
may I speak?

21:47.790 --> 21:48.270
Please.

21:49.270 --> 21:50.270
Today,

21:50.270 --> 21:52.420
I have two pieces of news to
share with everyone.

21:52.420 --> 21:53.280
First,

21:53.400 --> 21:54.400
Kuanli Group

21:54.400 --> 21:56.370
has launched a high-end fusion restaurant.

21:56.370 --> 21:57.370
As for the address,

21:57.370 --> 21:58.140
coincidentally,

21:58.140 --> 21:59.990
it's right opposite your hotel.

22:00.560 --> 22:02.120
As for the head chef,

22:02.510 --> 22:03.750
it's Jian Shikun,

22:03.750 --> 22:05.880
whom you recently kicked out,

22:05.880 --> 22:06.720
Chef Jia.

22:09.810 --> 22:10.890
Chef Jia has

22:10.910 --> 22:13.030
officially joined our group.

22:13.090 --> 22:16.150
He was promoted to
head chef of the Chinese restaurant.

22:19.100 --> 22:21.300
It's truly a case of
everyone in their right place,

22:21.300 --> 22:22.610
and getting what they need.

22:22.610 --> 22:23.670
Congratulations.

22:25.680 --> 22:27.710
Mr. Duan, as far as I know,

22:27.990 --> 22:30.080
the restaurant in your hotel

22:30.100 --> 22:32.280
targets high-spending customers.

22:32.310 --> 22:33.390
The service style

22:33.410 --> 22:35.060
is more like a club

22:35.090 --> 22:36.240
rather than a hotel.

22:36.260 --> 22:37.660
It also uses a membership system.

22:37.660 --> 22:39.550
These are two different tracks.

22:40.790 --> 22:42.180
As for Chef Jia,

22:42.250 --> 22:45.050
Purong Hotel doesn't plan to rehire him.

22:45.080 --> 22:46.140
So, congratulations.

22:46.140 --> 22:48.070
I hope you enjoy working together.

22:52.810 --> 22:54.330
That's a matter of opinion.

22:54.330 --> 22:55.710
There is a second issue.

22:55.790 --> 22:57.650
Kuanli Group

22:57.790 --> 23:00.530
signed a contract

23:00.670 --> 23:02.930
with the famous Chenying Design Studio.

23:03.820 --> 23:04.410
By the way,

23:04.410 --> 23:05.240
Mr. Ji,

23:05.440 --> 23:07.810
aren't you going to invite them

23:07.840 --> 23:10.920
as the design consultant
of Purong Chinese Restaurant?

23:10.920 --> 23:11.920
I'm sorry.

23:11.950 --> 23:12.980
In the end,

23:13.030 --> 23:14.690
they chose Kuanli.

23:14.720 --> 23:15.480
But I believe

23:15.480 --> 23:17.210
they will give you a reply soon.

23:18.850 --> 23:20.030
Thank you, Mr. Duan,

23:20.050 --> 23:21.950
for sharing information so selflessly.

23:21.950 --> 23:22.670
Yes.

23:22.770 --> 23:25.160
We did plan to cooperate with
Chenying Design Studio.

23:25.160 --> 23:26.100
However,

23:26.140 --> 23:28.380
this is just one of

23:28.410 --> 23:30.140
our overall renovation plans.

23:32.280 --> 23:33.390
I understand that everyone

23:33.390 --> 23:35.100
lacks confidence in

23:35.130 --> 23:36.330
our reopening.

23:36.350 --> 23:38.150
But what I want to tell you is that

23:38.170 --> 23:39.240
this is not a risk

23:39.720 --> 23:41.240
but an opportunity.

23:41.730 --> 23:43.920
I promise you all here

23:43.940 --> 23:47.030
that we will break even
within a month of reopening.

23:47.410 --> 23:48.480
For three consecutive months,

23:48.480 --> 23:50.010
we will remain profitable.

23:50.430 --> 23:51.680
If I fail to accomplish this task,

23:51.680 --> 23:52.440
I will

23:53.000 --> 23:54.200
resign voluntarily.

23:56.960 --> 23:59.140
This is a military pledge.

23:59.270 --> 24:00.720
It seems Mr. Ji is going to

24:00.720 --> 24:02.320
fight to the death this time.

24:04.200 --> 24:05.890
I don't think there is

24:06.270 --> 24:07.870
any need to be so aggressive.

24:07.870 --> 24:08.510
Anyway,

24:08.510 --> 24:09.640
Mr. Ji is also

24:09.870 --> 24:11.500
a management talent.

24:11.920 --> 24:12.640
Why do you

24:12.720 --> 24:15.000
risk your own career like this?

24:15.400 --> 24:16.160
Alright.

24:16.480 --> 24:17.920
I have heard

24:17.920 --> 24:19.180
both sides' opinions.

24:19.370 --> 24:21.430
I think we should end the discussion.

24:22.000 --> 24:22.830
Next,

24:22.830 --> 24:24.440
let's vote by show of hands.

24:24.830 --> 24:25.830
Those who agree with

24:25.830 --> 24:27.050
the Chinese restaurant's

24:27.050 --> 24:28.330
renovation plan,

24:28.360 --> 24:29.760
please raise your hands.

24:46.070 --> 24:47.620
Three voted in favor.

24:47.800 --> 24:49.150
Two voted against.

24:49.640 --> 24:51.660
The resolution on
the Chinese restaurant renovation plan

24:51.660 --> 24:52.550
passed.

24:52.770 --> 24:54.090
Let's call it a day.

24:58.640 --> 24:59.470
Aunt,

24:59.770 --> 25:00.890
isn't it too hasty?

25:00.920 --> 25:01.810
You are

25:02.030 --> 25:03.430
always so conservative.

25:03.570 --> 25:05.030
Overthinking everything

25:05.350 --> 25:06.610
won't let you succeed.

25:13.240 --> 25:14.720
Congratulations.

25:15.070 --> 25:15.720
Thank you.

25:26.000 --> 25:27.000
As for what you did

25:27.030 --> 25:27.480
this time...

25:27.480 --> 25:28.240
Mr. Wei,

25:28.260 --> 25:29.520
don't be discouraged.

25:29.590 --> 25:32.110
If we can kick Ji Feng out this time,

25:32.590 --> 25:34.190
we're halfway there.

25:51.660 --> 25:52.920
You want to eat yourself to death?

25:52.920 --> 25:54.050
Why did you get so much food?

25:54.050 --> 25:55.600
Didn't you see that?

25:55.750 --> 25:56.960
The cooks of the Chinese restaurant are

25:56.960 --> 25:59.480
cooking in our staff canteen.

26:03.870 --> 26:05.980
We are enjoying Michelin-level cuisine.

26:05.980 --> 26:08.150
When the Chinese restaurant reopens,

26:08.170 --> 26:09.480
your good days will be over.

26:09.480 --> 26:11.910
We don't even know when
the Chinese restaurant will be renovated.

26:11.910 --> 26:12.600
Reopening?

26:12.830 --> 26:14.790
You can wait until the cows come home.

26:14.790 --> 26:15.750
Didn't they say the board

26:15.750 --> 26:17.270
had approved Mr. Ji's plan?

26:17.270 --> 26:18.120
Miyu,

26:18.330 --> 26:20.650
since when do you care about gossip?

26:20.790 --> 26:21.270
I...

26:22.580 --> 26:23.510
Nonsense.

26:23.510 --> 26:26.160
Isn't everyone in the hotel
caring about it?

26:26.720 --> 26:27.790
Don't keep us in suspense.

26:27.790 --> 26:29.200
Hurry up and catch us up.

26:30.030 --> 26:31.160
The board

26:31.160 --> 26:32.460
did approve it.

26:32.600 --> 26:34.150
But I heard

26:34.270 --> 26:36.420
the renovation team
Mr. Ji wanted to cooperate with

26:36.420 --> 26:37.630
was snatched

26:37.660 --> 26:38.860
by Mr. Duan.

26:39.110 --> 26:42.360
No one knows what Mr. Ji is going to do.

26:43.480 --> 26:44.920
Everyone is very pessimistic about

26:44.920 --> 26:46.780
the Chinese restaurant project.

26:47.000 --> 26:48.140
Let's talk about something happy.

26:48.140 --> 26:50.200
Dianjiangchun is livestreaming tonight.

26:50.200 --> 26:52.070
Goods are available at up to 70% off!

26:52.070 --> 26:53.130
What does she sell?

26:53.270 --> 26:54.750
She doesn't just
sell cultural tourism products now.

26:54.750 --> 26:56.010
She sells everything.

27:21.610 --> 27:23.410
[AIA&LEED]

27:23.440 --> 27:26.070
[LIN & PARTNERS DESIGN ASSOCIATES]
[DANIEL TAN]

27:39.440 --> 27:40.120
Hello.

27:40.590 --> 27:41.990
Where is your forewoman?

27:42.000 --> 27:42.790
She is off work.

27:42.790 --> 27:44.390
Do you need me to contact her?

27:44.590 --> 27:45.240
It's fine.

27:46.130 --> 27:46.780
Thanks.

28:17.590 --> 28:18.270
Mr. Tan.

28:18.270 --> 28:18.920
Sorry to

28:18.920 --> 28:20.110
bother you so late.

28:20.140 --> 28:22.210
Then, why did you still come here?

28:24.990 --> 28:25.890
You won again.

28:27.680 --> 28:29.000
I bet with Mr. Tan.

28:29.030 --> 28:30.590
I said after you read his business card,

28:30.590 --> 28:32.120
you would definitely come.

28:32.150 --> 28:32.960
He said nobody would

28:32.960 --> 28:34.400
work after 10 p.m.

28:34.400 --> 28:35.000
See?

28:35.000 --> 28:36.240
What did I tell you?

28:38.790 --> 28:40.270
You have to keep your word.

28:41.070 --> 28:41.720
I promise.

28:42.200 --> 28:43.060
Please come in.

28:43.200 --> 28:43.680
Okay.

28:44.070 --> 28:44.750
I'll leave you to it.

28:44.750 --> 28:45.510
I'm leaving.

28:45.510 --> 28:46.170
Good night.

28:46.270 --> 28:46.920
Thank you.

29:08.080 --> 29:09.680
This kind of color matching of

29:09.680 --> 29:11.090
bright red and purple

29:11.110 --> 29:12.900
with high saturation
is not popular anymore.

29:12.900 --> 29:14.140
What is

29:14.160 --> 29:15.360
popular now?

29:15.590 --> 29:16.400
Warm,

29:16.400 --> 29:17.240
simple,

29:17.240 --> 29:18.480
wooden,

29:18.750 --> 29:19.680
gray,

29:19.680 --> 29:20.750
and so on.

29:21.590 --> 29:22.480
I remember

29:22.480 --> 29:24.070
the second floor of your hotel

29:24.070 --> 29:25.070
only has a few private rooms,

29:25.070 --> 29:25.750
right?

29:25.750 --> 29:26.920
Yes, there are 12 rooms in total.

29:26.920 --> 29:28.400
That's not enough.

29:28.590 --> 29:30.510
Young people nowadays like

29:30.750 --> 29:33.390
talking about work while eating.

29:33.410 --> 29:34.680
I suggest

29:34.710 --> 29:36.580
to build

29:37.070 --> 29:38.790
a new Chinese-style

29:39.030 --> 29:40.000
hollow-carved

29:40.410 --> 29:41.440
private room in the lobby.

29:41.440 --> 29:43.550
It won't block the view,

29:43.590 --> 29:45.380
while still offering
privacy.

29:45.400 --> 29:47.490
Since you are renovating the restaurant,

29:47.490 --> 29:48.340
we can be

29:48.510 --> 29:49.720
bolder.

29:50.400 --> 29:51.180
This way,

29:51.240 --> 29:52.510
the hotel will be more...

29:52.510 --> 29:53.670
Let me pour you another cup.

29:53.670 --> 29:54.880
No. No. No.

29:57.080 --> 29:59.320
Get me some alcohol

29:59.350 --> 30:00.860
to refresh my mind.

30:00.880 --> 30:01.750
No way.

30:02.750 --> 30:03.720
I caught you.

30:03.720 --> 30:05.720
You are trying to drink secretly again.

30:05.720 --> 30:06.520
This is my son.

30:06.920 --> 30:07.510
Mr. Tan, nice to meet you.

30:07.510 --> 30:08.830
He's a curator.

30:08.830 --> 30:10.690
I asked him to come and give some advice.

30:10.690 --> 30:11.490
We meet again.

30:11.790 --> 30:12.610
Sit.

30:12.990 --> 30:14.520
You seem to know each other.

30:15.280 --> 30:16.040
Yes.

30:16.060 --> 30:18.580
We met once abroad.

30:18.790 --> 30:20.000
It's destiny.

30:20.000 --> 30:20.720
That's great.

30:20.720 --> 30:22.650
We can have a discussion together.

30:27.240 --> 30:29.040
Then, I'll be straightforward.

30:29.680 --> 30:32.340
Can we change all the wall lamps
to chandeliers?

30:34.130 --> 30:35.040
Go on.

30:35.070 --> 30:36.240
I know that the current wall lighting

30:36.240 --> 30:37.590
provides very even illumination.

30:37.590 --> 30:39.160
But in a setting like a restaurant,

30:39.160 --> 30:40.480
it's more appropriate to use chandeliers.

30:40.480 --> 30:42.200
Because they can
focus a softer light source

30:42.200 --> 30:44.250
on the dining table area.

30:44.400 --> 30:45.890
Then isn't it easier to

30:45.910 --> 30:46.960
draw the guests' attention

30:46.960 --> 30:48.030
to the dishes?

30:48.590 --> 30:50.520
Also, from a spatial perspective,

30:50.590 --> 30:53.400
the current layout after adjustment

30:53.920 --> 30:55.320
looks a bit top-heavy.

30:55.510 --> 30:56.200
Right?

30:56.770 --> 30:58.770
If we use this vertical lighting,

30:58.800 --> 31:00.380
arranged in a scattered way like this,

31:00.380 --> 31:03.010
it can make the lighting and fixtures
more decorative.

31:03.010 --> 31:05.710
It will also make the whole place
look more coordinated.

31:05.710 --> 31:06.710
What do you think?

31:06.870 --> 31:07.940
He's a curator.

31:07.960 --> 31:09.680
He just brought his theories here.

31:09.680 --> 31:11.010
They're all connected.

31:12.970 --> 31:14.100
You are so serious.

31:14.790 --> 31:16.300
- What he said makes sense.
- Daniel.

31:16.300 --> 31:17.830
No, I don't want it.

31:17.830 --> 31:19.750
Try this cup. It's different.

31:20.960 --> 31:21.750
Try it.

31:27.360 --> 31:29.080
I added lemon and honey.

31:29.110 --> 31:30.770
Doesn't it taste much better?

31:31.070 --> 31:32.570
Not bad.

31:32.820 --> 31:34.620
Mr. Ji, you should have a cup too.

31:35.040 --> 31:36.410
Stop drinking coffee all the time.

31:36.410 --> 31:37.820
Honey cures headaches.

31:38.570 --> 31:39.210
Thank you.

31:40.600 --> 31:41.490
Mr. Tan.

31:41.510 --> 31:42.620
Long time no see.

31:43.720 --> 31:44.240
Long time no see.

31:44.240 --> 31:44.830
Thank you.

31:44.830 --> 31:45.960
I'll leave you to it.

31:55.560 --> 31:56.230
That makes sense.

31:56.230 --> 31:56.960
Yes.

32:16.590 --> 32:17.270
Mr. Ji.

32:17.960 --> 32:19.400
About Qiaoqi.

32:19.400 --> 32:20.600
I misunderstood you.

32:20.640 --> 32:21.320
I'm sorry.

32:21.880 --> 32:23.200
This brand of soothing tea

32:23.200 --> 32:24.750
can help relieve headaches.

32:24.750 --> 32:25.750
I hope it helps.

32:26.270 --> 32:27.070
Xu Miyu.

32:45.200 --> 32:46.000
Ms. Xu.

32:48.270 --> 32:49.550
Tomorrow at 8 a.m.,

32:49.550 --> 32:51.030
the crew will come to the VIP entrance

32:51.030 --> 32:52.550
to shoot Qiao Feifei.

32:52.550 --> 32:54.680
There will be many reporters present.

32:54.690 --> 32:56.680
I need you to coordinate the service well.

32:56.680 --> 32:57.680
Can you handle it?

32:58.000 --> 32:58.550
Yes.

32:59.070 --> 33:00.870
Are there any special requests?

33:01.300 --> 33:02.400
Stars are also guests.

33:02.400 --> 33:03.640
Just serve them

33:03.640 --> 33:05.370
like you serve any other guest.

33:05.440 --> 33:06.000
For this kind of thing,

33:06.000 --> 33:08.240
I don't need to teach you
step by step, right?

33:08.240 --> 33:09.040
I understand.

33:17.480 --> 33:19.960
[Only You, Feifei]

33:19.960 --> 33:23.920
[You Are My Ideal]

33:31.350 --> 33:32.350
Room service.

33:34.440 --> 33:35.160
Ou.

33:35.260 --> 33:36.440
I'm looking for Dai Wei

33:36.440 --> 33:37.200
to coordinate with him

33:37.200 --> 33:39.060
on tomorrow morning's schedule.

33:39.070 --> 33:40.310
He's already back at the studio.

33:40.310 --> 33:41.760
He won't be coming over today.

33:41.760 --> 33:42.400
Then, could you

33:42.400 --> 33:44.150
give me his contact info?

33:44.510 --> 33:45.680
I'm afraid not.

33:45.680 --> 33:47.440
Wei usually hands out
his own business cards.

33:47.440 --> 33:48.640
We can't just give out

33:48.640 --> 33:49.830
his contact info.

33:51.690 --> 33:52.550
How about this?

33:52.570 --> 33:54.500
The crew arrives at 8 a.m. tomorrow.

33:54.500 --> 33:56.350
I'll call you guys at 7:30, okay?

33:56.380 --> 33:56.950
Okay.

33:57.100 --> 33:57.920
Bye.

33:57.920 --> 33:58.480
Okay.

33:59.150 --> 34:03.170
[You Are My Ideal]

34:16.150 --> 34:17.070
Room service.

34:20.710 --> 34:21.630
Room service.

34:26.889 --> 34:27.940
Butler Xu.

34:28.120 --> 34:28.960
What is it?

34:28.980 --> 34:30.980
Your VIP pass is ready.

34:31.010 --> 34:32.659
So fast.

34:33.760 --> 34:34.510
Thank you.

34:34.530 --> 34:35.520
You're welcome.

34:35.670 --> 34:37.620
By the way, tomorrow at 8 a.m.,

34:37.639 --> 34:39.620
a crew will be filming downstairs.

34:39.639 --> 34:41.080
At the VIP entrance,

34:41.110 --> 34:42.230
there will be some media.

34:42.230 --> 34:44.630
It might cause some inconvenience
to your travel.

34:44.630 --> 34:45.489
Sorry for that.

34:46.550 --> 34:47.750
Qiao Feifei's shoot?

34:50.670 --> 34:51.360
Got it.

34:51.510 --> 34:52.480
I'll leave now.

35:08.230 --> 35:09.710
When the crew's cars arrive later,

35:09.710 --> 35:10.710
let them park over there.

35:10.710 --> 35:12.310
See those two parking spots?

35:13.590 --> 35:15.390
Don't just focus on stargazing.

35:15.400 --> 35:16.590
Be careful with everything.

35:16.590 --> 35:17.440
Got it?

35:17.510 --> 35:18.670
Don't worry, Miyu.

35:18.670 --> 35:19.630
I promise to complete the task.

35:19.630 --> 35:20.760
I won't let you down.

35:20.830 --> 35:21.390
I swear.

35:21.970 --> 35:23.700
I'll go attend to other things.

35:33.510 --> 35:34.440
Room service.

35:36.480 --> 35:37.280
Wait a minute.

36:03.190 --> 36:04.390
Miyu, the car is here.

36:04.870 --> 36:05.970
[Only You, Feifei]

36:05.240 --> 36:05.880
Copy that.

36:07.880 --> 36:08.800
Room service.

36:10.960 --> 36:11.960
Room service.

36:13.630 --> 36:14.360
Wait a minute.

36:14.360 --> 36:15.840
It's already 7:40.

36:16.210 --> 36:17.340
I need to see Dai Wei.

36:18.060 --> 36:19.200
Feifei,

36:19.490 --> 36:20.740
I told you not to wear

36:20.770 --> 36:22.100
this vintage Mugler.

36:22.380 --> 36:23.560
For an occasion like today,

36:23.560 --> 36:26.220
you must wear the outfit
specified by the brand.

36:26.910 --> 36:27.880
Be a good girl.

36:27.900 --> 36:29.450
We can't breach the contract.

36:29.450 --> 36:30.240
Dai Wei.

36:30.430 --> 36:31.580
Excuse me.

36:31.920 --> 36:33.480
It's already 7:40.

36:33.500 --> 36:34.630
The crew has arrived.

36:34.630 --> 36:35.590
And for some reason,

36:35.590 --> 36:37.000
a lot of fans and media are here too.

36:37.000 --> 36:37.510
I...

36:37.650 --> 36:38.710
Why are you rushing me?

36:38.710 --> 36:39.630
Please

36:39.730 --> 36:40.640
help me

36:40.670 --> 36:41.940
get a dress of this brand.

36:41.940 --> 36:42.870
The black one

36:42.900 --> 36:44.360
in that pile of suitcases.

36:48.320 --> 36:49.880
Shasha called and asked for you.

36:49.880 --> 36:51.010
Why are you rushing?

36:51.150 --> 36:52.610
Can't you see I'm trying to
figure something out?

36:52.610 --> 36:54.590
My brain will explode
if you keep pushing me.

36:54.590 --> 36:54.960
Miyu.

36:54.960 --> 36:56.280
Is Qiao Feifei downstairs yet?

36:56.280 --> 36:58.110
The media and followers
are blocking the entrance downstairs.

36:58.110 --> 36:59.440
It's a complete mess.

37:00.290 --> 37:01.030
I know.

37:01.030 --> 37:02.160
I'll push her again.

37:03.440 --> 37:04.320
Did you find it?

37:04.760 --> 37:05.560
Dai Wei,

37:05.580 --> 37:07.260
it's almost 8:00 now.

37:07.500 --> 37:08.860
Can we...

37:08.890 --> 37:09.670
Found it!

37:11.880 --> 37:12.440
Hurry up.

37:12.570 --> 37:13.820
Take Feifei to change.

37:13.820 --> 37:15.700
When is Miyu coming down?

37:16.630 --> 37:18.720
Does the only thing you could do
is to push people?

37:18.720 --> 37:19.670
Instead of rushing us,

37:19.670 --> 37:21.460
why don't you help us find the clothes?

37:21.460 --> 37:22.470
Someone

37:22.590 --> 37:23.440
should have coordinated with us

37:23.440 --> 37:25.020
on this yesterday, right?

37:25.170 --> 37:27.710
Does your hotel
lack this basic professionalism?

37:27.710 --> 37:28.190
Yesterday, I...

37:28.190 --> 37:29.230
What's to explain?

37:29.230 --> 37:30.510
Instead of explaining to me,

37:30.510 --> 37:31.840
why don't you arrange some security guards

37:31.840 --> 37:33.570
to maintain order downstairs?

37:34.800 --> 37:35.490
Dressed!

37:35.760 --> 37:36.230
Hurry up.

37:36.230 --> 37:37.430
Let's go downstairs.

37:37.510 --> 37:38.570
We're coming down.

37:43.230 --> 37:44.920
Why aren't they here yet?

37:53.640 --> 37:54.600
Coming.

37:55.480 --> 37:56.400
Let's go.

37:56.400 --> 37:56.960
Turn it on.

37:56.960 --> 37:57.920
Turn it on. Let's go.

37:57.920 --> 37:58.780
Wait.

37:59.040 --> 38:00.170
It's not Feifei.

38:00.270 --> 38:01.830
Li Bingyan, go!

38:01.960 --> 38:02.360
Wait.

38:02.360 --> 38:03.690
Qiao Feifei isn't here.

38:04.590 --> 38:05.600
Li Bingyan.

38:05.630 --> 38:06.440
Ms. Li Bingyan,

38:06.440 --> 38:07.960
is the man next to you your boyfriend?

38:07.960 --> 38:09.280
Is he also in the industry?

38:09.280 --> 38:10.880
How long have you been together?

38:10.880 --> 38:11.480
Please answer our questions.

38:11.480 --> 38:12.070
Please answer us.

38:12.070 --> 38:12.930
Just answer us.

38:13.800 --> 38:15.780
Why are there so many of you here?

38:16.180 --> 38:18.150
Wait, it's not Qiao Feifei.

38:19.030 --> 38:19.710
It's cold.

38:19.710 --> 38:21.370
You should wear more clothes.

38:34.550 --> 38:35.440
Ms. Li Bingyan,

38:35.440 --> 38:36.880
is the man next to you your boyfriend?

38:36.880 --> 38:38.360
How long have you been together?

38:38.360 --> 38:39.000
Please answer us.

38:39.000 --> 38:39.760
Please answer us.

38:39.760 --> 38:41.710
We are not ready to tell everyone yet.

38:41.710 --> 38:42.070
Darn it.

38:42.070 --> 38:43.930
Tell us about your relationship.

38:44.480 --> 38:45.320
Please answer us.

38:45.320 --> 38:46.290
When were you together?

38:46.290 --> 38:47.810
It's really not convenient to disclose.
